      "content": "i just don't have the time or the patience for a blood test right now, and honestly i'm just looking for a quick fix so i don't feel like a zombie. if i just do the 50k IU for exactly 10 days and then stop, it's basically just a temporary spike, right? chances of getting actual toxicity in just 10 days seem really low compared to the benefit of getting my energy back. what do u think, is it worth the risk for a short period?",
